parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to the non-deployment of airbags in the event of a crash, increasing the risk of injury or fatality.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates

the airbag system fails to detect an occupant in the passenger seat
and the airbag system malfunctions or fails to deploy in a crash.
